author: Indhukrishna
body:
## Steps to reproduce

Picked the latest build from AppVeyor https://ci.appveyor.com/project/PowerShell/PowerShell/build/artifacts 
Installed the MSI
## Expected behavior

MSI is installed and PowerShell works
## Actual behavior

MSI is installed. But there is no content inside the folder. 
## Environment data

Cannot get environment data since PowerShell is not even installed. 

It looks like the PR #1742 broke the build. AppVeyor is not building Release configuration but the changes for this PR is assuming that it is.
title: Build from AppVeyor does not have any content inside
